      "properties": {},
      "widgets_values": [
        "## Game-Engine Packing\n\nRemove BG \u2192 **SAM3** isolates parts \u2192 per part: **greyscale \u2192 normalize luma \u2192 center median** (each object's luma balanced *within its own mask*) \u2192 packed two ways:\n\n- **BD Pack Channels** \u2014 R=lips, G=teeth, B=tongue in one RGB texture\n- **BD Atlas Pack** \u2014 the same balanced parts tiled into a grid atlas (cols\u00d7rows, padding, `layout` JSON has per-cell UV rects)\n\nSwap the SAM3 prompts + add channels/cells for your own parts (e.g. the LipViseme atlas)."
      ],
      "title": "\u2139\ufe0f About \u2014 \ud83e\udde0 BrainDead Game-Engine Packing"
    }
